autoRebalancePancake((int24,int24,uint24.details: Flow:  1) (best-effort) unstake in adapter.gauge, if any.  2) exitPositionToVault -> funds return to this vault.  3) optional swap via fixed dexRouter (if swapAmountIn > 0).  4) reopen position using all idle balances in [newLower, newUpper].  5) (best-effort) restake position via adapter. Security:  - Only the pre-defined `executor` may call this function.  - Automation must be enabled by the owner.  - cooldwonSec is enforced against lastRebalanceTs.  - tokenIn/tokenOut must be the pool tokens (adapter.tokens()).  - If allowSwap == false, swapAmountIn must be 0.

params.params: Struct containing rebalance parameters computed off-chain.

claimRewards().details: Adapter should be implemented to send rewards directly to this vault.

collectToVault().details: Only owner can trigger; fees remain in the vault as idle balances.

params._adapter: Concentrated liquidity adapter already wired to a pool.
params._allowSwap: Whether automation is allowed to execute swaps.
params._dexRouter: Fixed DEX router used for swaps.
params._feeCollector: Protocol fee collector (future performance fee hook).
params._maxSlippageBps: Initial max slippage in basis points.

exitPositionAndWithdrawAll(address).details: - Closes the position (if any) via the adapter. - Transfers all token0 and token1 balances held by this vault to `to`. - Future performance-fee logic can be added here before sending funds out.

returns.cooldown: Cooldown in seconds between automated rebalances.
returns.swapAllowed: Whether automation is allowed to execute swaps.

openInitialPosition(int24,int24).details: Only callable by the owner. Will revert if no funds.

returns.tokenId: Current tokenId held by this vault in the adapter.

params.cap0: Maximum amount of token0 to use (0 = use all available).
params.cap1: Maximum amount of token1 to use (0 = use all available).

setAutomationConfig(uint32,uint16,bool).details: These values are used by the off-chain executor as hard bounds      and can also be enforced on-chain in future iterations (e.g., with quotes).

params._allowSwap: Whether automation is allowed to perform swaps.
params._maxSlippageBps: Maximum slippage allowed in basis points.

params.enabled: True to enable, false to disable.

swapExactInPancake(address,address,uint2.details: - Apenas o owner pode chamar. - Usa sempre o `dexRouter` imutvel. - Mantm os fundos dentro do vault (recipient = address(this)). - til para converso pontual (ex.: rewards -> USDC para   contabilizar em convert_gauge_to_usdc no backend).

params.sqrtPriceLimitX96: Limite opcional de preo (0 = sem limite).

adapter().notice: Concentrated liquidity adapter (Pancake, Uniswap, Aerodrome, etc.).

allowSwap().notice: Whether automated logic is allowed to execute swaps.

automationEnabled().notice: Whether automation is enabled for this vault.

claimRewards().notice: Claim rewards from the underlying gauge/farm.

cooldownSec().notice: Minimum time (in seconds) between automated rebalances.

dexRouter().notice: Fixed DEX router used for swaps (no arbitrary routers allowed).

exitPositionAndWithdrawAll(address).notice: Exit the position and withdraw all vault balances to `to`.

exitPositionToVault().notice: Exit the position, keeping resulting tokens in the vault.

feeCollector().notice: Address that will receive protocol performance fees (future hook).

getAutomationConfig().notice: Returns the current vault configuration for automation.

lastRebalanceTs().notice: Timestamp of the last successful automated rebalance.

maxSlippageBps().notice: Maximum allowed slippage in basis points (informational / future on-chain checks).

openInitialPosition(int24,int24).notice: Open the initial position using all idle balances in the vault.

positionTokenId().notice: Last tokenId held by this vault in the adapter.

positionTokenIdView().notice: Minimal positionId view for off-chain bots/APIs.

rebalanceWithCaps(int24,int24,uint256,ui.notice: Manual rebalance using caps (advanced owner operation).

setAutomationEnabled(bool).notice: Enable or disable automation for this vault.

stake().notice: Stake the current position in the underlying gauge/farm (if any).

swapExactInPancake(address,address,uint2.notice: Swap manual via Pancake V3 usando o router fixo do vault.

tokens().notice: Returns the pool tokens for this vault's adapter.

unstake().notice: Unstake the current position from the underlying gauge/farm (if any).
